{
  "texts": [
    "Many works that follow the traditional architecture (Li et al. 2020; Rao et al.",
    "2022a; Florez et al. 2021; Meng et al.",
    "2021; Rasmy et al. 2021; Zeng et al.",
    "2022; Shome 2021; Darabi et al. 2020; Prakash et al. 2021) include a classification/prediction layer as the way of conducting, for example, the fine-tuning process in their specific domains.",
    "Meanwhile, the other 14 works presented more complex modifications."
  ]
}